casebody.data:
Atkins, Appellee, v. Chudowsky, Appellant.

[Cite as Atkins v. Chudowsky, 98 Ohio St.3d 1209, 2003-Ohio-1013.]

(No. 2001-2166 Submitted February 11, 2003 Decided March 19, 2003.) Kenneth R. Hurley, for appellee. D. Chris Cook, for appellant.

{¶ 1} The cause is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently allowed.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Wolff, Lundberg Stratton and O’Connor, JJ., concur. William H. Wolff Jr., J., of the Second Appellate District, sitting for Cook, J.
